description: The Possoni continue with their family tradition in this contemporary-style restaurant situated opposite the long-established Ma.Ri.Na. Here, their emphasis is on the quality of their ingredients, namely fresh fish and seafood that they use to prepare a broad range of dishes, some simple and traditional in style, while others are more complex and creative.
